ActCanadian High Arctic Research Station Act
PrecisAppointment of JENNIFER C. HUBBARD of Chelsea, Quebec, to be President of the Canadian High Arctic Research Station, to hold office during pleasure for a term of five years, on a full-time basis, effective December 10, 2020.
